  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9c\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bc8 -\u00a0\u0bb9\u0bc6\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb9\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The consequences of forcibly arresting a citizen on an airplane without just cause are grave - Hector Abuhamy",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The consequences of forcibly arresting a citizen on board an aircraft without reasonable cause can be grave.",
        "United People's Shakti Member of Parliament Hector Appuhamy said that such activities have increased the dissatisfaction with Sri Lanka among the international community.",
        "He stated this at a press conference held at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo on Wednesday (27) while he further mentioned,",
        "Emergency law was imposed and arrests increased. Forcible arrest of a person who was willing to board a flight without any valid reason is a violation of basic human rights. Due to such activities, the dissatisfaction of foreign countries towards Sri Lanka has increased.",
        "The consequences of this action are graver than those of empty-faced protesters being attacked.",
        "At present, fuel distribution is being carried out in such a way as to paralyze the activities of the people. The government has taken steps to restrict the daily activities of the people by distributing fuel in limited quantities.",
        "The current President Ranil Wickremesinghe is acting on the basis that there is no need to be accountable to the people.",
        "The ongoing human rights abuses in the country will further delay IMF assistance. Therefore, after August 15th, we will face severe crisis in fuel import.",
        "The only solution to such problems in the country is to hold general elections soon. In the present situation, an all-party government cannot be formed under the leadership of this government. We cannot participate in it. That is why we are insisting that the elections be held quickly, he said."
      ],
